<P><HI>Jones</HI> fell into Raptures with this good Gentleman; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">nd when after much Per&s;wa&s;ion, they found the Fa|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">er grew &s;till more and more irritated, in&s;tead of ap|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">ea&s;ed, <HI>Jones</HI> conducted the Uncle to his Nephew at <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="2 letters">e Hou&s;e of Mrs. <HI>Miller.</HI></P>
