<P><Q REND="inline">'Ay, all of us, quoth the Squire; nay, it was n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="2 letters"> Propo&s;al of mine. She knows it was her Aunt pro+po&s;ed it to me fir&s;t.&mdash;Come, <HI>Sophy,</HI> once mo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="2 letters"> let me beg you to be a good Girl, and gee me you<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"> Con&s;ent before your Cou&s;in.'</Q></P>
